# Student Performance Analysis 🎓

A beginner Pandas project for analyzing student performance data using Python.

## 🚀 Features
- Data Cleaning
- Score Analysis
- Gender-wise Analysis
- Study Time Analysis
- Parent Education Analysis

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas

## 📂 Files
- `student.py`
- `student_data.csv`

## ▶️ Run
```bash
python student.py
```

